<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 space-y-24">
    
    <!-- Hero Block -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-luxury-900 text-luxury-200 text-[10px] font-display font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                🌿 Sourced from Jammu & Kashmir
            </div>
            <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-luxury-950 leading-tight">
                Crafting the Old Ways of Pure Agriculture
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-luxury-600 leading-relaxed">
                Deenz Organics wasn't born in a commercial conference room. We were founded in the mountain loam of <strong class="text-luxury-950">Wanpora, Kulgam, Jammu & Kashmir</strong>, alongside Pahalgam and Pampore. Our founders, the brothers Deen Mohd and Raashid Din, established our central office and sorting facility in Wanpora, Kulgam to ensure that absolute premium, single-origin Kashmiri organic produce could be packaged directly at the source and delivered fresh to families across India and worldwide.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-luxury-600 leading-relaxed">
                We reject industrial heat washing, cheap sulfur chemical preserving, and blending different harvest regions. When you crunch our walnut kernels or smell our sun-dried garlic, you are experiencing Kashmir exactly as nature crafted it.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="h-64 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md relative group border border-stone-200">
                <img src="/assets/images/kashmiri_farm_orchard.webp" alt="Pahalgam Valleys, Jammu & Kashmir" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white text-[11px] font-display font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-black/40 px-3 py-1 rounded backdrop-blur-sm">
                    🏔️ Sourced from Naibasti, Pahalgam
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-luxury-950 text-luxury-200 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl space-y-6 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-48 h-48 bg-luxury-500/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
                <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white">Our Harvest Pillars</h3>
                
                <div class="space-y-4 text-xs">
                    <div class="flex gap-3">
                        <span class="text-xl">🏔️</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Single-Origin Guarantee</h4>
                            <p class="text-luxury-300">Every single packet is grown inside Pahalgam and Pampore valleys with zero commercial dilution.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-3">
                        <span class="text-xl">☀️</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Traditional Silt & Irrigation</h4>
                            <p class="text-luxury-300">Nourished strictly by nutrient-dense river silt from cold Himalayan glacial runoff.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-3">
                        <span class="text-xl">🤝</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Fair Farmer Compensations</h4>
                            <p class="text-luxury-300">We pay local J&K farmers up to 35% above market rates for their premium graded selections.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Founder's Address -->
    <div class="bg-white border border-luxury-200/60 rounded-3xl p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center shadow-sm">
        <div class="md:col-span-4 flex justify-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-luxury-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-2xl text-luxury-800 shadow-inner">
                DM
            </div>
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-luxury-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-2xl text-luxury-800 shadow-inner">
                RD
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-4">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-luxury-950">A Message from the Founders</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-luxury-600 leading-relaxed italic">
                "Our valleys produce some of the finest walnut trees and organic garlic cloves on earth, but conventional bulk supply chains mix and dry them carelessly, destroying the essential Omega-3 fatty oils and deep aromatic defense layers. At Deenz Organics, we manage the entire chain from plantation grading to vacuum sealing right in our hometown. We promise 100% honesty."
            </p>
            <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-luxury-950">Deen Mohd & Raashid Din</p>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-luxury-400">Co-Founders, DEENZ ORGANICS</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
